ps://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/zipball/6.0.0", "body": "This is a new major release of AppIntro. Please note that this release contains multiple new features (see below), several bugfixes, as well as multiple breaking changes.\r\nTo get a deeper overview of the breaking changes, please read the [migration document](/docs/migrating-from-5.0.md).\r\n\r\n## Summary of Changes\r\n\r\n* The library is now 100% in Kotlin! \ud83c\udf89.\r\n* Target SDK is now 29.\r\n* The UI was completely revamped and refactored.\r\n* You can now request permissions on AppIntro without having to lock the slide.\r\n* The library has now 14 more translations.\r\n\r\nThe full changelog is available in the [CHANGELOG file](/CHANGELOG.md)\r\n\r\n## How to update\r\n\r\nThis release contains several breaking change.\r\nPlease read them all in the [migration document](/docs/migrating-from-5.0.md)\r\n\r\n1. **Add the JitPack repository to your build file**\r\n\r\n```\r\nrepositories {\r\n    maven { url \"https://jitpack.io\" }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n2. **Add the dependency**\r\n\r\n```\r\ndependencies {\r\n    implementation 'com.github.AppIntro:AppIntro:6.0.0'\r\n}\r\n```", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/26141634/reactions", "total_count": 1, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 1, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}}
{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/13613456", "assets_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/13613456/assets", "upload_url": "https://uploads.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/13613456/assets{?name,label}", "html_url": "https://github.com/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/tag/v5.1.0", "id": 13613456, "author": {"login": "paolorotolo", "id": 5623301, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjU2MjMzMDE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5623301?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo", "html_url": "https://github.com/paolorotolo", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "node_id": "MDc6UmVsZWFzZTEzNjEzNDU2", "tag_name": "v5.1.0", "target_commitish": "master", "name": "AppIntro 5.1.0", "draft": false, "prerelease": false, "created_at": "2018-10-23T17:08:30Z", "published_at": "2018-10-23T17:12:55Z", "assets": [], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/tarball/v5.1.0", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/zipball/v5.1.0", "body": "## Changelog\r\n * **Fixed issue that caused a build failure on Kotlin projects** (#597);\r\n * Added support for Android 8.0 custom Fonts API (#590);\r\n * Updated Translations;\r\n * Miscellaneous bug fixes and performance improvements;\r\n\r\n## How to update\r\n\r\n1. **Add the JitPack repository to your build file**\r\nAdd it in your root build.gradle at the end of repositories:\r\n```gradle\r\nallprojects {\r\n    repositories {\r\n\t...\r\n\tmaven { url 'https://jitpack.io' }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n2. **Add the dependency**\r\n```gradle\r\ndependencies {\r\n         implementation 'com.github.paolorotolo:appintro:v5.1.0'\r\n}\r\n```"}
