{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/7132848", "assets_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/7132848/assets", "upload_url": "https://uploads.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/7132848/assets{?name,label}", "html_url": "https://github.com/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/tag/v4.2.1", "id": 7132848, "author": {"login": "avluis", "id": 875593, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjg3NTU5Mw==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/875593?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis", "html_url": "https://github.com/avluis", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/avluis/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "node_id": "MDc6UmVsZWFzZTcxMzI4NDg=", "tag_name": "v4.2.1", "target_commitish": "main", "name": "AppIntro 4.2.1", "draft": false, "prerelease": false, "created_at": "2017-07-22T14:44:01Z", "published_at": "2017-07-22T15:00:14Z", "assets": [], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/tarball/v4.2.1", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/zipball/v4.2.1", "body": "## How to update\r\nTime for a quick update!\r\nAs per the last release, we switched from Maven to [JitPack.io](https://jitpack.io/#apl-devs/appintro/).\r\nUpdating AppIntro is very simple.\r\n\r\n1. **Add the JitPack repository to your build file**\r\nAdd it in your root build.gradle at the end of repositories:\r\n```gradle\r\nallprojects {\r\n    repositories {\r\n\t...\r\n\tmaven { url 'https://jitpack.io' }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n2. **Add the dependency**\r\n```gradle\r\ndependencies {\r\n    compile 'com.github.apl-devs:appintro:v4.2.1'\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Changelog\r\n### Features\r\n * [Initial SliderPage implementation](https://github.com/apl-devs/AppIntro/issues/466)\r\n * Add method to hide Pager Indicator. (#457)\r\n\r\n### Bugfixes\r\n * Fix permission request on last slide (#416)\r\n * Code cleanup/refactoring! (#428)\r\n * Fix IndexOutOfBoundsException when no slides are passed (#455)\r\n \r\n\r\n**Thanks to all contributors who made this release possible!**\r\n"}
{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/6512174", "assets_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/6512174/assets", "upload_url": "https://uploads.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/6512174/assets{?name,label}", "html_url": "https://github.com/AppIntro/AppIntro/releases/tag/v4.2.0", "id": 6512174, "author": {"login": "paolorotolo", "id": 5623301, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjU2MjMzMDE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5623301?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo", "html_url": "https://github.com/paolorotolo", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/paolorotolo/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "node_id": "MDc6UmVsZWFzZTY1MTIxNzQ=", "tag_name": "v4.2.0", "target_commitish": "master", "name": "AppIntro 4.2.0", "draft": false, "prerelease": false, "created_at": "2017-05-26T07:51:31Z", "published_at": "2017-05-26T08:26:15Z", "assets": [], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/tarball/v4.2.0", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/AppIntro/AppIntro/zipball/v4.2.0", "body": "## How to update\r\nIn this release we switched from Maven to [JitPack.io](https://jitpack.io/#apl-devs/appintro/).\r\nUpdating AppIntro is even more simple.\r\n\r\n1. **Add the JitPack repository to your build file**\r\nAdd it in your root build.gradle at the end of repositories:\r\n```gradle\r\n\tallprojects {\r\n\t\trepositories {\r\n\t\t\t...\r\n\t\t\tmaven { url 'https://jitpack.io' }\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}\r\n```\r\n\r\n2. **Add the dependency**\r\n```gradle\r\n\tdependencies {\r\n\t        compile 'com.github.apl-devs:appintro:v4.2.0'\r\n\t}\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Changelog\r\n### Features\r\n * Add Translations (French, Indonesian, Russian, Turkish, Arabic);\r\n * Add RTL Support;\r\n * Add back button navigation; \r\n * Add *showSeparator()* method;\r\n * Allow users to change Bar color in AppIntro 2;\r\n * Refreshed Example app;\r\n * Dependencies update;\r\n\r\n### Bugfixes\r\n * Check NPE on views (#361);\r\n * Fix issues with ProGuard (#337);\r\n * Fix Custom Typefaces issues (#318);\r\n * Fix page indicator when the page change listener is overridden (#316);\r\n\r\n**Thanks to all contributors who made this release possible!**\r\n"}
